reviews.text: I was craving McDonald's at around 1:10 at night as I was taking the last light rail (615p) so I decided to get off at Leung King and have some Meal #4. My first visit here. Late night so... the seat that I sat on smelled. Not of food, smelled damp and unclean. The staff couldn't speak English so they had to call someone from the back to take my order. No big deal but touch screens would be a nice addition here considering this is a big McDonald's. There are lots of seats. Oh and the fries were soft and soggy.
Ordinary mcdonalds fast food. Even the fries were too soft to eat.
在2018年尾的今天，仍然可以用3個幾美元的價錢，享受一頓營養成份均衡，味道可口的早晨全餐，實在超值！
很好 就是人比較多 😎
食物好好味及有4小時免費wifi使用。
